title: Magic Butt - Interactive ass! v1.05
description:
A live wallpaper with a sexy girl that reacts to touching and shaking your phone or tablet.
If you're a guy:
Testing confirmed that Magic Butt makes girlfriends extremely jealous.

If you're a girl:
Testing also confirmed that giving Magic Butt to a boyfriend gives the girl a chance to finally rest.

Supports multitouch screen and accelerometer (for shaking).
Doesn't ask for any unnecessary permissions.
There are no ads.

When you install Magic Butt, it is bound to your Google account, so you can use it on as many devices (Android phones and tablets) as you want to.

Copy protection is disabled, so you can install Magic Butt on a device with root access.

We use Google Play licensing service, so the internet connection is required during the first launch. Also, license is sometimes re-checked; we're not sure, how often would it be, because the whole process is managed by Google Play licensing server.

What's in this version : (Updated : Jun 30, 2013)

- Auto-dismiss when clicked for one-time-ever "please rate" and "like it" notifications (as opposed to manual dismiss in previous versions using "clear" GUI button which possibly wasn't present on some devices).
- Performance optimization allowing smooth animation on slower devices.
- Increased picture quality - now without visible color contours in gradients.
- 2 more physical parameters to adjust in the options menu.
